fileSamples.statement: (sig : signature) : subtype (proj_sig_res sig) (typ_rpair mreg_type (loc_result sig)) = true.
fileSamples.proofString:
unfold loc_result.
destruct (proj_sig_res sig); destruct Archi.big_endian; auto.

fileSamples.statement:
(sig : signature) : subtype (proj_sig_res sig)
  (typ_rpair mreg_type
     match proj_sig_res sig with
     | Tlong => if Archi.big_endian then Twolong R0 R1 else Twolong R1 R0
     | Tint | Tany32 => One R0
     | _ => One F0
     end) = true.
(s1 s2 : signature) (H : sig_res s1 = sig_res s2) : loc_result s1 = loc_result s2.
fileSamples.proofString:
unfold loc_result, proj_sig_res.
rewrite H; auto.

fileSamples.statement:
(s1 s2 : signature) (H : sig_res s1 = sig_res s2) : match proj_xtype (sig_res s1) with
| Tlong => if Archi.big_endian then Twolong R0 R1 else Twolong R1 R0
| Tint | Tany32 => One R0
| _ => One F0
end =
match proj_xtype (sig_res s2) with
| Tlong => if Archi.big_endian then Twolong R0 R1 else Twolong R1 R0
| Tint | Tany32 => One R0
| _ => One F0
end.
